# Claude Code Desktop — environment configuration
#
# Point the Claude Agent SDK at your Portkey gateway. Both vars are passed
# straight through to the underlying Anthropic SDK.
#
# Portkey example:
ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.portkey.ai/v1
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-portkey-virtual-key-here
#
# Direct Anthropic (no Portkey):
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
